    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🛍️ Shopify Product Sync — Workflow C\n\n**Runs:** Every Sunday at 6:00 AM AEST (20:00 UTC Saturday)\n**Also triggered:** Via dashboard 'Sync from Shopify' button\n\n**What it does:**\n1. Fetches all active products from Shopify Admin API\n2. Filters products that have at least one image\n3. Normalises: category, price, image URL, in-stock status\n4. Clears and rewrites the Products tab in Google Sheets\n5. Sends Telegram confirmation with product count\n\n**Products Tab columns (in order):**\nProduct ID | Title | Vendor | Price | Image URL |\nProduct URL | Category | In Stock | Synced At | Featured\n\n**Setup Required:**\n- Replace SHOPIFY_CREDENTIAL_ID with Shopify_AMGO credential\n- Replace GSHEETS_CREDENTIAL_ID with GoogleSheets_AMGO credential\n- Replace TELEGRAM_CREDENTIAL_ID with Telegram_AMGO_Bot credential\n- Replace GOOGLE_SHEET_ID\n- Replace TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID",
        "height": 568,
        "width": 520,
        "color": 5
      },
